TENDL-2025 (TALYS Evaluated Nuclear Data Library)                 1325 1451   11
                                                                  1325 1451   12
Charged particle general purpose library                          1325 1451   13
                                                                  1325 1451   14
Author: A.J. Koning, IAEA                                         1325 1451   15
                                                                  1325 1451   16
Ref.: A.J. Koning, D. Rochman, J.-Ch. Sublet, N. Dzysiuk,         1325 1451   17
      M. Fleming, and S. van der Marck, TENDL: Complete nuclear   1325 1451   18
      data library for innovative nuclear science and             1325 1451   19
      technology, Nuclear Data Sheets 155, 1 (2019).              1325 1451   20
